# Changelog

All notable changes to this project will be documented in this file.

The format is based on [Keep a Changelog](https://keepachangelog.com/en/1.0.0/),
and this project adheres to [Semantic Versioning](https://semver.org/spec/v2.0.0.html).

## [Unreleased]




## [1.0.0] - 21.07.2023

### Fixed

- Multiple undos one after another now possible
- Errorhandling concerning clientnames (":" not allowed)

### Changed

- Minor visual changes


## [0.3.0] - 19.07.2023

### Changed

- server and client can be started from same application
- Default values for textfields to prevent problems

### Added

- More shapes 
- Image import that only works for the actual client -> No networking functionality


### Removed

- Fill functionality
- weird icon


## [0.2.9] - 16-07-2023

### Fixed 

- a lot of Bugs and problems
- logger problems and improvements


## [0.2.8] - 26-06-2023

### Added 

- More colors to choose from
- paintlog gets deleted after canvas clear 


## [0.2.7] - 25-06-2023

### Added

- First steps to add drawing functions other than "line"
- Radio buttons that draw shapes on click


## [0.2.6] - 25-06-2023

### Added

- gitignore file

### Changed

- undo/redo and redraw for increased efficiency and functionality

- UI to look more appealing


## [0.2.5] - 22-06-2023

### Added 

- undo/redo function 

### Fixed

- Errors regarding undo/redo and Networking 


## [0.2.4] - 19-06-2023

### Changed

- Extracted the logic for buttons and
  client-server-communication out of UiBuilder into
  new class ActionHandler.java


## [0.2.3] - 12-06-2023

### Fixed

- Error regarding client name


## [0.2.2] - 12-06-2023

### Fixed

- Color and Line Width are transmitted


## [0.2.1] - 12-06-2023

### Fixed

- Drawing process is now visible for all clients.


## [0.2.0] - 12-06-2023

### Added

- ability to draw squiggly lines


## [0.1.1] - 04-06-2023

### Added

- Image save / Export functionality


## [0.1.0] - 08-05-2023

### Added

- live drawing on the canvas (only straight lines)

### Fixed 

- Errors regarding delay on sharing the stroke 


## [0.0.5] - 07-05-2023

### Added

- login scene

### Removed

- unused Classes


## [0.0.4] - 06-05-2023

### Added

- Actual Network functionality


## [0.0.3] - 03-05-2023

### Added

- Classes to lay Networking foundation


## [0.0.2] - 19-04-2023

### Added 

- Ability to Change line color
- Ability to Change line Width
- Ability to Auto fill shapes with last color
- Ability to Clear the entire canvas


## [0.0.1] - 12-04-2023

### Added

- Update Readme
- Create IntelliJ project
- Basic paint functionality


